ack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-bfu","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":43235,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/18\/travel-appoint-leader\/","url_meta":{"origin":43244,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Appoint leader for traveling group","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khurdi reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhenever three people set out on a journey, let one of them be appointed as their leader.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2608 Grade: Hasan (authentic) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37362,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/11\/dhikr-najwa\/","url_meta":{"origin":43244,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Remembering Allah as a private conversation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 11, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, retreated within the mosque and he heard them raising their voices in recitation. The Prophet lifted the curtain and he said, \u201cAre not all of you in private conversation with his Lord? Do not bother each\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31763,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/parents-make-them-laugh\/","url_meta":{"origin":43244,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Parents: Return to your parents, make them laugh","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cI have come to pledge allegiance to you upon emigration, and I left my parents weeping.\u201d The Prophet said, \"Return to them and make them laugh, just as you\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36374,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/28\/who-in-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":43244,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Prophets, martyrs, children in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hasna' bint Mu'awiyah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Prophet is in Paradise, the martyrs are in Paradise, the young children who die are in Paradise, and the infant buried alive is in Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2521 Grade: Hasan (fair) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34523,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/27\/evil-within-greed-cowardice\/","url_meta":{"origin":43244,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Vice: Evil within people lies in greed and cowardice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe worst evil within a man is his restless greed and his utmost cowardice.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2511 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40780,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/08\/09\/division-from-shaytan\/","url_meta":{"origin":43244,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Unity: Separation and division is from the devil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 9, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Tha\u2019labah reported: The people would set up camp and disperse into the trails and valleys. The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThis scattering of yours into the trails and valleys is from Satan.\u201d They never set up camp afterward unless they were close to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0